This finely styled knee-length coat is trimmed with elegant embroidery work. It can be dressed up for the more formal gentleman, or simplified for the more common man depending on the fabrics, accessories, and colors chosen. Styles are available for both men and women.
A copy of this item (including any crafting you do on it) is used by your Bottled Companion.

Most owls have big heads, stocky bodies, soft feathers, short tails, a sharply hooked beak, and a reversible toe that can point either forward or backward. Owl's eyes are big and round and face forward, like humans do. Most owl species are active at night, not in the daytime.

IMPORTANT NOTES:

-You can only copy armor appearances to your armor if the base AC matches.

-You can make a whole new outfit from scratch with this model and purchase it. The cost is a bit more than what you can sell it for, but less than you'd have to buy a blank one for.

-Modifications are otherwise entirely free!]
